{"error": null, "result": {"nr": 14, "upvote_ids": [], "change_log": [{"type": "create", "when": "2015-03-03T06:55:48Z", "uid": "i6ry1ln7xRU", "data": "i6sxyqakzb43ey", "anon": "no"}, {"uid": "hdjoucuyb836fq", "to": "i6sxyqahoex3ex", "when": "2015-03-03T07:50:09Z", "anon": "no", "data": "i6szwmkvhl417d", "type": "i_answer"}, {"type": "followup", "to": "i6sxyqahoex3ex", "when": "2015-03-04T03:41:07Z", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "anon": "no"}, {"type": "followup", "to": "i6sxyqahoex3ex", "when": "2015-03-05T11:06:09Z", "uid": "i6um7uuk5ka1z6", "anon": "no"}], "q_edits": [], "i_edits": [], "unique_views": 162, "bookmarked": 5, "config": {}, "history": [{"subject": "80386 实模式 1M寻址", "content": "<p>   看资料 80386的实模式下PA = cs  * 16 &#43; ds &#xff0c;网上说是1M寻址空间 但是1M = 2^20 我就好奇这1M是怎么算出来的</p>", "created": "2015-03-03T06:55:48Z", "uid": "i6ry1ln7xRU", "anon": "no"}], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "request_instructor_me": false, "folders": ["lab1"], "type": "question", "tag_good": [], "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-03-03T06:55:48Z", "t": 1433499921038, "id": "i6sxyqahoex3ex", "status": "active", "tag_good_arr": [], "default_anonymity": "no", "my_favorite": false, "bucket_order": 2, "is_bookmarked": false, "is_tag_good": false, "bucket_name": "Today", "no_answer_followup": 0, "children": [{"folders": [], "bucket_order": 2, "config": {}, "history": [{"subject": "", "content": "<p>所有与x86 CPU相关的问题都可以查阅Intel的Architecture Software Developer&#39;s Manual&#xff08;简称SDM&#xff09;&#xff1a;<a href=\"http://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/processors/architectures-software-developer-manuals.html\">http://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/processors/architectures-software-developer-manuals.html</a>。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>有关实模式的内容&#xff0c;参见第一卷3.3.1节和第三卷20.1节&#xff0c;简而言之&#xff0c;实模式下只支持1M的寻址空间。</p>", "created": "2015-03-03T07:50:09Z", "uid": "hdjoucuyb836fq", "anon": "no"}], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "bucket_name": "Today", "is_tag_endorse": false, "children": [], "tag_endorse": [], "tag_endorse_arr": [], "created": "2015-03-03T07:50:09Z", "id": "i6szwmksn7h17c", "type": "i_answer"}, {"no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "bucket_name": "Week 3/1 - 3/7", "bucket_order": 8, "updated": "2015-03-04T03:41:07Z", "config": {}, "anon": "no", "data": {"embed_links": null}, "folders": [], "subject": "<p>CS和IP都是16位&#xff0c;CS左移4位&#xff0c;加到一起只有20位。20位二进制数的表示范围就只有2^20&#xff0c;这就是1024*1024&#xff0c;也就是1M.</p>", "children": [], "type": "followup", "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-03-04T03:41:07Z", "id": "i6u6g88rxx0os"}, {"no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "i6um7uuk5ka1z6", "bucket_name": "Week 3/1 - 3/7", "bucket_order": 8, "updated": "2015-03-05T11:06:09Z", "config": {}, "anon": "no", "data": {"embed_links": null}, "folders": [], "subject": "<p>根据PA = CS * 16 &#43; IP&#xff0c;实际可以寻址的最大地址应该是CS=0xFFFF并且IP=0xFFFF&#xff0c;这个地址超过了1MB。在80286之前&#xff0c;因为地址总线只有20位&#xff0c;所以&#xff0c;实际访问的地址是PA % 1MB的结果&#xff0c;也就是如果地址计算结果超过1MB&#xff0c;实际访问的内存会绕回到低地址。在80286中&#xff0c;地址总线被扩充到24位。当地址总线扩充之后&#xff0c;一些依靠这种trick的DOS程序会出错&#xff0c;IBM为了保持PC的兼容性&#xff0c;在主板上的A20总线增加了一个门电路&#xff0c;称之为A20 Gate。在开机默认状态下&#xff0c;A20 Gate是关闭的&#xff0c;此时A20地址线始终保持0&#xff0c;保证了向后的兼容性。通过特殊的方法&#xff0c;可以将A20 Gate开启&#xff0c;此时就可以自由访问所有内存。在众多开启A20 Gate的方法中&#xff0c;一种是使用键盘控制器8042的一个未被使用的管脚来当作A20 Gate的控制线&#xff0c;ucore使用的就是这种方法。</p>", "children": [], "type": "followup", "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-03-05T11:06:09Z", "id": "i6w1sdpgvfw469"}], "request_instructor": 0, "tags": ["lab1", "student"], "s_edits": [], "num_favorites": 0}, "aid": "iajgua32rlc38d"}